content: Hi Rowan, I saw you are with Gamma Labs in Houston. Which big ideas keep getting pushed because no one has time?
Why should I tell him that?
Fair question. I am curious what is working well for you right now.
Well, literally, why do I tell you that? Who are you? I don't even know you.
I am with Cloumen, we help labs like yours automate busywork. what is one task that eats up your team is time?
If you want me to end the call, please say exactly: end call now. Otherwise, how can I help?
Well, I said that I... I should have told you anything about the company like what? Taking my team's time or anything, why should I tell you that?
You are right to be careful. What is one small daily hassle your team faces?
What is in it for you?
If we can save your team time, we earn a chance to help. What is one manual job you wish was automatic?
